b19b5ba343fcc6a879e3d4bfd461e0d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/solv/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">solv</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 23, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Really great plugin with awesome support.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fits all your needs and incredible secure! Best Form-Plugin out there.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mrsnowman/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9bf1886e233b558ae78ad513f768a4e9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9bf1886e233b558ae78ad513f768a4e9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mrsnowman/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mrsnowman</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 23, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">First of all, I have to mention it is<strong> very secure</strong>, because all the uploads from the forms are optional <strong>CHMOD protected</strong>! They are not just dumped into the uploads folder of WP. No public accessing via URL, No hotlinking, no brower-sniffig for filenames... The most secure Form-Plugin I have in use!<br /><br />It is incredible well documented (Docs and Videos). <strong>It has field logic and calculation</strong>, that makes your form dynamic like no other! And comes with plenty more of hand picked features that makes it easy for you to get the forms in shape and workflow as you like.<br />Formidable is created from devs, that know whats a form needs. And I mean you can create really sophisticated forms for pre-production tasks.<br /><br />And I not even mentioned the \"Views\", the \"Reports\" or the options to <strong>create entire PDFs</strong> from forms to ship around via mail for further tasks in your company. Did I mentioned the <strong>e-mail routing via dropdown fields</strong>? No? You\'ll love it!<br /><br />I know, this review looks like \"bought\" but it isn\'t, I was using Kaliforms for a long time, but some issues, that could not be solved, where \"standard\" in Formidable. <strong>So I switched... and boy... I should have done this years ago!</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Top of the list for creating and using forms</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/docamg/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4b61873b1d1d724f730532971ddf41f5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4b61873b1d1d724f730532971ddf41f5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/docamg/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">docamg</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 22, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Wonderful plugin for creating forms. Simply the best. Great templates. Easy to use. Look no further</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Woo Product Forms Issues After Domain Change</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tonin66/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/76482c26393b373b417324cfe594ec44?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/76482c26393b373b417324cfe594ec44?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tonin66/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tonin66</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 16, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">I developed a site on a temp domain running WooCommerce with Formidable Pro and also the WooCommerce add-on installed. There are forms attached to my products that were required to be filled out before being able to go to the cart. After changing the domain name to launch the site you can now bypass filling out the forms and click the button to go to the cart page on those products. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">When I changed the domain, I used the Woo tools to clean products and clear out all the transients, user sessions, etc., then went back into each product to update it so that they were available on the site again. Even Formidable support can\'t figure out why the forms are not required anymore. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Has anyone else experienced anything like this and if so, how did you fix it? </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">outstanding support - problem solved</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tkutscher/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e42b9a0c8a446ebaa805123ae005c7db?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e42b9a0c8a446ebaa805123ae005c7db?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tkutscher/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tkutscher</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 16, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Very friendly and helpful support. My problem was not a trivial one but it was solved within a day. Further more, the support was always in reach and the communication very effective. You can count on Formidable Forms! thanks so much - keep up the good work</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Solved the issue</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jackthemark/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9fa063551fbbbfdb31132e9a827d80c3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9fa063551fbbbfdb31132e9a827d80c3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jackthemark/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jackthemark</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 14, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">The Formidable customer service team provided quick solutions to my problem.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Just wanted to mention how great the app and the service is once again!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mat29303/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a921033fccf595a61fe69921a46f80f1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a921033fccf595a61fe69921a46f80f1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mat29303/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mat29303</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 13, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Since I discovered this plugin, it makes wonders for me, I am now more knowledgable than ever with formidable forms and it enables me to do anything I want easily, I am always impressed myself by the end results. And what to say about the service, just amazing support! Thank you Formidable Team for you excellent work!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great tool, as simple as that</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sle20/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ee0797831dd126d20bde1667f80ba3f8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ee0797831dd126d20bde1667f80ba3f8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sle20/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">SLE2.0</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 13, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Using this tool for at least 10 years, so this is enough to say we like it and more importantly recommend it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent tool with very cooperative support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"s